  "description": "PhysioMotion_Artifact is an EEG dataset organized according to the Brain Imaging Data Structure (BIDS) standard. The dataset contains electrophysiological recordings with associated physiological motion artifact annotations, designed to support research on artifact detection and removal in EEG analysis. This resource facilitates the development and validation of artifact handling methods in neuroimaging studies.",
